node.text: I am absolutely loving all of these Fall pieces from @eloquii ! Eloquii has partnered up with @walmartfashion to provide us with affordable fashion pieces under $50 sizes 14-28! Eloquii elements will be sold on Eloquii.com, and Walmart.com! They have pieces for every occasion such as errands, PTA meetings, or just stay cute and comfy for your zoom meetings. Which one was your favorite? #ad #eloquiielements Shop Here: http://liketk.it/2Wgo0 and link of my bio!

node.text: Some days I want to be out with friends and family but other days I want to stay home and have a me day. I do this because spending time alone with myself helps me relax my mind and take a break from the outside world. During this time, I hang out with Pepe (my puppy), I meditate, and pamper myself ! Even if it’s just to watch my favorite show, it’s important to slow down and reset. Remember to always take a break, we’re only human. Most comfortable loungewear from @TargetStyle #IChoose #ad

TUNE IN TOMORROW FRIDAY AUGUST 27TH at 3:00 PM EST time  ON MY PAGE FOR A LIVE TRY ON HAUL @MARIACASTELLANOS_RI AND I ARE DOING FOR OUR ENTIRE COLLECTION

node.text: August, the last month of Summer! I am trying to take in as much of the sun as I can. I don’t usually get in the water when I go to the beach but this time I did and it felt amazing. Sometimes, anxiety makes you not want to do things but #IChoose to do things that are out of my comfort zone so that I can grow as a person. You never know until you try. Beautiful cover up from @TargetStyle #ad
